text: Pielavesi is a municipality in Northern Savonia, Finland. As of 28 February 2023, 4,137 people lived there. Neighbouring municipalities are Iisalmi, Keitele, Kiuruvesi, Maaninka, Pihtipudas, Pyhäjärvi and Tervo. == Other websites == * Municipality of Pielavesi – Official website Category:Municipalities of North Savo
